{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"696-rain-rain","title":"Rain, Rain","description":"Roll along with the cloud as it brings rain and joy!","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Manisha Chaudhry"],"illustrators":["Ajit Narayan"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/696-rain-rain"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/790870/size3/6cce451176ed21d91d7cbf567d30f1c0.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/790870/size6/6cce451176ed21d91d7cbf567d30f1c0.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/8743/size6/4a76145e7beb91fff2c10f65f9baa71b.jpg","text":"A cloud rolled along merrily in the sky.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/8744/size6/3135a8e1073c74bce26f50245c4216d2.jpg","text":"The peacock said, “Why don’t you rain? I will dance for you.”","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/8745/size6/63ff43e947322a615f08887759ffc037.jpg","text":"The fish said, \"Please rain. I need more water.\"","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/8746/size6/5bdb3d47b093b96939a9a5ad7c2fd45b.jpg","text":"The farmer said, “Please rain. I’ll plant seeds for the next crop.”","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/8747/size6/3f0a57199dec0237eef8309980514262.jpg","text":"Raju said, “If you rain, I’ll sail paper boats.”","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/8748/size6/8fd45f41b465249650ca93bf92d04c6a.jpg","text":"The cloud rained in a shower of shimmering drops.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/8749/size6/4565dba217f4aed7be9cb51fd123460c.jpg","text":"The peacock spread its pretty feathers and danced.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/8750/size6/f4bee299690e8353c4636bfe107bd05a.jpg","text":"The pond filled up. The fish was happy.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/8751/size6/c9c57b020cec0f1b07044edb59ccefd2.jpg","text":"The farmer started planting seeds.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/8752/size6/13eefcbc569c958f5ae5453232cb7bb0.jpg","text":"Splish! Splash! Splosh! Raju and his friends had a wonderful time in the puddles.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/8753/size6/fb21885f9ec50b5c040c56623e7cb82b.jpg","text":"The cloud filled everybody's heart with joy. It moved on. All the children waved goodbye.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":109}}